Not that getting into <COREF ID="11" TYPE="IDENT">town</COREF> was easy .
Storm flooding caused back - ups on the freeway , and many commuters had to find rides to <COREF ID="3" TYPE="IDENT">BART 's</COREF> stations , because parking lots were full before dawn .
